reviewText:
Early Access Review

I recommend this game, but only to those who like the genre. If you like Runescape, Ragnarok, and Minecraft, this is the game for you. I started to play this game because of a bad review I read. At the time it was overwhelmingly positive, with only a couple negative reviews. The worst negative review I could find read;

This game is too difficult

